text: Urs Niedhart (born 11 September 1969) is a Swiss skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Switzerland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
